		{
			"id": "http://endonend.micro.blog/2018/10/13/what-i-can.html",
	      	
			"title": "What I Can Control",
			
			"content_html": "<p><a href=\"https://www.swiss-miss.com/2018/10/what-i-can-control.html\">swissmiss – What I Can Control</a> →</p>\n\n<p>Absolutely love this… I made and printed out a version of this to display in our house. Good reminders for adults and kids alike.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-i-can-control\">What I Can Control:</h3>\n\n<ol>\n  <li>My Actions &amp; Reactions</li>\n  <li>My Boundaries</li>\n  <li>My Expectations</li>\n  <li>How I Invest My Time</li>\n  <li>How I Treat Myself</li>\n  <li>How I Treat Others</li>\n</ol>\n",
			"date_published": "2018-10-13T10:16:30-04:00",
			"url": "https://www.endonend.org/2018/10/13/what-i-can.html"
		},
		
