		{
			"id": "http://endonend.micro.blog/2018/10/04/a-few-weeks.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>A few weeks ago I asked if anyone ever <a href=\"https://www.endonend.org/2018/09/21/has-anyone-ever.html\">deleted their entire Apple Music collection and started over</a>. Well, I just did. Re-booting and adding back with purpose and mindful of the all-you-can-eat world we live in now. Before: 44,000+ songs. Current: 1,486 and a focus on quality.</p>\n",
			"date_published": "2018-10-04T09:36:54-04:00",
			"url": "https://www.endonend.org/2018/10/04/a-few-weeks.html"
		},
		
